🎯 Task: Smart Access Control System
You’re building logic for a building entry system.

📥 Inputs:
int hour;            // 0–23
boolean hasCard;
boolean isEmployee;

⚙️ Behavior:
If user doesn’t have a card → immediate denial
If user is an employee:
Allowed from 06:00 to 22:00
If user is not an employee:
Allowed from 09:00 to 18:00

📤 Output examples:
Access denied: No card
Access denied: Outside allowed hours
Access granted